Package inputmdxml.temporary

Contains auxiliary elements to store temporary conversion results
Author:
dschoenicke
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TemporaryAttribute
    TemporaryAttribute extends the UmlAttribute with additional fields for the 'association' and 'aggregation' attributes of the OwnedAttribute
    TemporaryModel
    Auxiliary class managing references of UmlElements, UmlTemplateParameters, UmlRelationships, UmlAttributes and UmlParameters
    These references are used for the replacement with the actual elements
    TemporaryRelationship
    Auxiliary class extending the UmlRelationship with references to the client element and supplier element since the resolving of all references is only possible after all UmlElements have been converted
    TemporaryTemplateBinding
    Extends the UmlTemplateBinding with a map containing references to the UmlTemplateParameter and type of the UmlTemplateBindings parameter substitution
